遊行爭取到 <br />\n打警犬可以制衡佢地氣勢<br />\n其次好多唔係鳩打 <br />\n有幾個係義士俾佢地壓咗係地下 <br />\n佢地係救緊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後 大家唔洗再回樓主<br />\n起一起底就知和理非黎 <br />\n亦唔好屌佢 各有各做</span>"},{"pid":"303fad0490f473ec0c151cab1c6c0c2d13af60dc","tid":1320280,"uid":111271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"你比人打唔還手?"},{"pid":"f47947df8703166c6d4f89e8ec12c9b151eacc56","tid":1320280,"uid":64487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"咁你話知點樣至可以達到五大訴求？<br />\n唱歌？鳩坐？遊行？"},{"pid":"53875b53510bf2ab432eaf9e101c0005b7fea476","tid":1320280,"uid":14299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"舉高手比狗咬 你傻撚左?"},{"pid":"cfaefd42667868f295fa2cd8519a450d24777bd0","tid":1320280,"uid":159083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"究竟打市民可以達到乜野目的？<br />\n<br />\n你話比我知。<br />\n<br />\n七大警察目標同抱負，邊一樣係必須要靠打市民達成？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抱負<br />\n<br />\n使香港繼續是世界上其中一個最安全及穩定的社會<br />\n<br />\n目標<br />\n<br />\n為確保社會安穩，香港警隊務必：<br />\n<br />\n維護法紀<br />\n維持治安<br />\n防止及偵破罪案<br />\n保障市民生命財產<br />\n與市民大眾及其他機構維持緊密合作和聯繫<br />\n凡事悉力以赴，力求做得最好<br />\n維持市民對警隊的信心</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFROM 警犬官網"},{"pid":"ac37649db137ab856fd9a2b678b50eff0b6fab87","tid":1320280,"uid":31317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"究竟打市民可以達到乜野目的？"},{"pid":"120f3024aff71979ebe8da25e90d670fba6cd3e7","tid":1320280,"uid":244691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e9b4a8b8c7dbe0fd84c8e7a3307d69d44b7abb6","tid":1320280,"uid":11698,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVDeW1P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVDeW1P.png&h=57cd64a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hK6L3GQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/